These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, cabbage, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, august, december
House: modern, cottage, victorian, farmhouse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, daisy, iris
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, red, blood-red, ebony
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the farmhouse house is between the person eating eggplant and the person who likes ebony##2
 3. the person who growssunflower is the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is between the person eating eggplant and the victorian house##2
 6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who likes red is the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the modern house is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Food           | cabbage | eggplant   | pumpkin | pineapple |
| Birthday   | april      | october | august              | december |
| House   | modern       | cottage     | farmhouse               | victorian    |
| Flower           | balloon-flower        | daisy     | iris           | sunflower       |
| Color     | red | blood-red     | yellow                | ebony      |

