 2. the person who likes red is on the right of the wooden house##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is between the futuristic house and the thai##2
 4. the person who likes lilac is the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the italian is the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the left of the american##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the futuristic house##1
12. the wooden house is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
