 3. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching musical movies##2
 4. the person playing poker is the prince-smoker##1
 5. the person eating spinach is the havana-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person playing canasta is the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
11. the person eating lemon is between the havana-smoker and the person playing canasta##2
12. the person eating raspberry is between the person playing poker and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | musical      | sports         | thriller | western      |
| Cigar           | havana | pall-mall | davidoff | prince     |
| City   | prague         | hamburg          | nizza  | san-francisco |
| Food         | spinach        | lemon  | raspberry | kiwi   |
| Game     | monopoly    | whist         | canasta     | poker     |

