.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, lemonade, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat, old-henry, swisher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, december, june
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, balloon-flower, tulip
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, collecting, writing
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking tea is the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person drinking water is between the swisher-smoker and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
