.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, dunhill, oliveros
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, 7up, mirinda
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, lavender, lilac
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, december, july
4 different games are played: domino, chess, canasta, poker
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who likes ivory##1
 2. the person playing poker is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 3. the person playing chess is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person playing canasta##2
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the havana-smoker is the person who likes apricot##1
11. the person who likes apricot is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | dunhill  | game | oliveros | havana |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | sprite   | 7up      | water    |
| Color   | ivory  | lavender | lilac        | apricot     |
| Birthday         | october  | february  | december     | july      |
| Game     | domino | poker      | chess   | canasta       |

 